Avoid mixing combinations, and be wary that combining mundane extracted items can lead to negative values. Good luck!

message: To get 100 points, use the 'filter' tool on a magical gas or liquid ingredient to get a 'processed magical' item. Then, use the 'vial' tool on a mundane solid ingredient to get a 'processed mundane' item. Finally, combine these two processed items (the filtered magical liquid and the extracted mundane liquid) to create the 100-value item. Avoid mixing raw ingredients or combinations that don't follow this processed-mundane + processed-magical pattern, as they often result in negative values.
